{"tid":1238854,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求幫幫忙！反送中抗爭 聲音及空間體驗嘅研究及問卷","createTime":"2019-06-18T03:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T03:35:17.000Z","uid":256647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"caca11d3df7cd7796cb8cfd614ea50cc7b01aaae","tid":1238854,"uid":256647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:20:26.000Z","msg":"借朋友account post：<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思各位，可唔可以借各位少少位同埋少少時間：<br />\n<br />\n我係UPenn（即係Trump果間）嘅doctoral research fellow，做緊有關今次<strong>「反送中」抗爭嘅聲音及空間體驗嘅研究及問卷調查</strong>。連結：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/W55ZGHD7Lrfa343G6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FW55ZGHD7Lrfa343G6&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXkngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=a4f0006a\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/W55ZGHD7Lrfa343G6</a><br />\n<br />\n我同我助手喺維園同金鐘派左超過900份 questionnaire guideline，但係得好少人做左問卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，可能因為大家當時上唔到網而且無心情 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，返到屋企太攰唔記得左，又可能在場有D人會懷疑我係咪扮做academic research但可能係黑警嘅spy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />⋯⋯我唔係呀！！我真係好真心想做好呢個研究 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，呢個係我嘅專長，除左上街外，呢個係我可以在我個崗位發揮的作用！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n長話短說，麻煩各位可唔可以花5-10分鐘填妥問卷，並傳給有出席嘅朋友們！<br />\n唔好意思要你地睇咁大篇嘢！！打搞哂各位巴打絲打！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本人感激不盡！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再post 條link：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/W55ZGHD7Lrfa343G6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FW55ZGHD7Lrfa343G6&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXkngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=a4f0006a\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/W55ZGHD7Lrfa343G6</a><br />\n<br />\nPS．問卷有少少我嘅簡介以確保大家能查核我無偽裝身分以及個research係真嘅，但請大家高台貴手，唔好起我底放上黎⋯⋯ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（我之前派問卷guideline果時有人說叫我放上黎連登，但因為怕被起底所以考慮左好耐⋯）<br />\n<br />\n麻煩哂！！多謝哂！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，辛苦哂，香港人！！！<strong>我地要繼續團結、加油！！！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>希望我地同烈士盼望嘅香港會來臨。</strong>"},{"pid":"635ea1014ae5d8d7d080d5189ce683c4ad8221d1","tid":1238854,"uid":256647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:25:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7cff294f9ff43f3157a6ea4ff66d4c196b3923f","tid":1238854,"uid":256647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:27:18.000Z","msg":"原來會沉得好快 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推！！"},{"pid":"6d722143845cf429d3228e9b1648118c9ef145ca","tid":1238854,"uid":256647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:28:46.000Z","msg":"PUSH!!!"},{"pid":"e9def2086ad4c3e0c0c28d34f39852ec770788c3","tid":1238854,"uid":256647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:30:02.000Z","msg":"PUSHHHHH!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"1ddcd1804c934b6f0b1c6b7d3ec1af7757d3793c","tid":1238854,"uid":256647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:30:32.000Z","msg":"push!!"},{"pid":"cc233378e8ea2a100f4cc2f2769ffa9a5e0f393e","tid":1238854,"uid":256647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:32:00.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"f8a5c2268e9e8b8a237f534f721f403d8c83571b","tid":1238854,"uid":256647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:33:44.000Z","msg":"push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ced275456269a0445e46a8a7605b421f339638","tid":1238854,"uid":256647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite